lead_paragraph: Brooke Schulte scored 21 points, Jacqui Grant added 19 and No. 18 DePaul easily beat No. 11 Syracuse 108-84 in the third-place game at the Gulf Coast Showcase on Sunday night.

headline.print_headline: No. 18 DePaul Hits 19 3's, Rolls Past No. 11 Syracuse 108-84
